Mobile Device Management (MDM) secures mobile devices (smartphones/tablets; excludes laptops/basic phones) accessing enterprise data in a perimeter-less world. Key concepts:
- MDM: Device config/security/remote admin.
- EMM: Umbrella incl. MDM + MAM + MTD.
- MAM: App/data control (BYOD-friendly).
- MTD: Detects malware/phishing/network threats.
